{"type":"message","id":"3a34d157","parentId":"4bb1e3dc","timestamp":"2026-02-22T01:20:08.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron event that contains some system messages about WhatsApp gateway connectivity and a cron error. Let me analyze what's happening:\n\n1. WhatsApp disconnected twice (status 408 and 428) and reconnected both times - these are just connectivity issues that resolved automatically\n2. A cron job error occurred: \"搜索API不可用，让我直接抓取财经网站资讯\" (Search API unavailable, let me directly grab financial website news)\n\nThis seems to be from a scheduled news/crypto/financial news fetcher that was trying to use a search API but it failed, so it tried to fall back to direct web scraping.\n\nThe user should know about:\n- The WhatsApp disconnects/reconnects (minor, resolved automatically)\n- The cron error with the search API failing\n\nLet me relay this information in a helpful way.","thinkingSignature":"db74be14b601b78a832f6e41a37a6aa166eedf31848eb7a723145c6407c2206c"},{"type":"text","text":"Cron 任务执行情况：\n\n1. **WhatsApp** - 断连两次（状态码 408 和 428），但都自动重连了，目前正常。\n\n2. **定时资讯抓取** - 搜索API不可用，任务尝试直接抓取财经网站作为备选方案。\n\n整体来看没有大问题，WhatsApp 已恢复正常连接。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":244,"cacheRead":3046,"cacheWrite":8486,"totalTokens":11804,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771723200982}}
