{"type":"message","id":"959e8218","parentId":"98687741","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:28:32.048Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lykcx5vzgubz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.19-2 (45d9b20) — I'm basically a Swiss Army knife, but with more opinions and fewer sharp edges.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2756,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.19-2 (45d9b20) — I'm basically a Swiss Army knife, but with more opinions and fewer sharp edges.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771727312044}}
