{"type":"message","id":"d9c4157f","parentId":"ced4f344","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:28:52.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issues:\n\n1. **SMTP 认证问题** - 163邮箱返回 \"User has no permission\" 错误，邮件无法发送\n2. **执行超时** - 任务执行时间过长（超过10分钟），导致超时\n3. **mail 命令问题** - `mail: unrecognized option '-v'`\n\n用户说一次都没成功过，确实如此。问题是：\n1. 邮件发送失败 - SMTP认证问题\n2. 任务超时 - 可能是因为抓取网站太慢\n\n让我检查一下邮件配置和任务设置，看看能否解决。","thinkingSignature":"1d1372f47738d4b2ece68af5c967cd44bb931653bc8d2c28dc5160bf7e62da70"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4ql0ue3pd3u9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /root/.openclaw/workspace/.env 2>/dev/null | grep -i mail || echo \"无.env文件\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2836,"output":170,"cacheRead":11401,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14407,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771727323474}}
