{"type":"message","id":"a55c2019","parentId":"00019914","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:29:17.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the HTML report is being generated successfully, but email sending is failing. The issues are:\n\n1. **SMTP认证失败** - 163邮箱需要授权码，不是登录密码\n2. **Timeout** - 默认超时太短，任务经常超时\n3. **mail命令问题** - 使用的mail命令不支持某些选项\n\nLet me fix the cron job to have a longer timeout and fix the email issue. First, let me check if there's an email configuration somewhere or if we need to set up proper SMTP.\n\nActually, I think the main issue is that the task is using the `mail` command directly which doesn't work well. We should either:\n1. Fix the SMTP configuration\n2. Use a different method to send emails\n\nLet me check what email options are available and update the cron job with a longer timeout.","thinkingSignature":"05f03a85308d0f41a2ebf45628c88faad12adfc97d2b8f7e7bee7d2bacfeb167"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，确实问题比较多。让我分析一下：\n\n**问题根因：**\n1. **SMTP认证失败** - 163邮箱返回 `User has no permission`，说明没正确配置授权码（不是登录密码）\n2. **执行超时** - 默认超时太短（30秒），抓取网站经常超时\n3. **mail命令不兼容** - 系统的mail命令不支持`-v`选项\n\n**好消息：** HTML报告其实**生成成功了**，只是邮件发不出去。\n\n我来修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dkpspqk31x2u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron edit 31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9 --timeout-seconds 600 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":5042,"output":335,"cacheRead":11401,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16778,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771727347618}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecc7fe8f","parentId":"a55c2019","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:29:20.093Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dkpspqk31x2u_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"name\": \"A股每日资讯\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1771426816719,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1771727360007,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"expr\": \"10 9 * * *\",\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日期。\\n\\n【重要要求】\\n1. 【关键】只抓取过去24小时内的新闻（例如，今天是2026年2月20日，所以只抓取2月19日至2月20日的资讯，不要抓取2月18日及更早的新闻！）\\n2. 必须从【至少4个不同来源】抓取资讯：第一财经、东方财富、新浪财经、同花顺、财联社、每日经济新闻等\\n3. 【不要放链接】- 将资讯要点直接总结展示在邮件正文中，每条资讯需要包含【标题+100字左右的内容摘要】\\n4. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-final.html 作为样式模板\\n5. 每个板块至少精选【TOP 10条】重要资讯（必须是最新24小时内的）\\n6. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\\n7. 【邮件发送】：必须以MIME text/html 格式发送邮件，确保邮件显示为渲染后的HTML页面\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"email\",\n    \"from\": \"nohotnnn@gmail.com\",\n    \"to\": \"qn_home@163.com\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771809000000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1771722600005,\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 600021,\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 6,\n    \"lastError\": \"Error: cron: job execution timed out\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2902,"aggregated":"{\n  \"id\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"name\": \"A股每日资讯\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1771426816719,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1771727360007,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"expr\": \"10 9 * * *\",\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"se