{"type":"message","id":"e3ca1663","parentId":"9645face","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:31:02.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No SMTP config in the docs. The issue is clear now:\n\n**Email delivery is not configured in OpenClaw.** The cron job has `channel: email` set, but there's no email plugin/channel enabled.\n\nLooking at the cron job config again:\n- `delivery.channel`: \"email\"\n- `delivery.from`: \"nohotnnn@gmail.com\"  \n- `delivery.to`: \"qn_home@163.com\"\n\nBut there's no email channel in OpenClaw's configuration, so it falls back to trying to send via Telegram (which fails because \"qn_home@163.com\" is not a valid Telegram chat ID).\n\nI need to either:\n1. Add email support to OpenClaw (if possible)\n2. Change the delivery method to something that works (like Telegram)\n3. Or configure the cron job to just save the HTML file and then manually send it\n\nLet me explain this to the user and propose a solution.","thinkingSignature":"000aa391c3b079a545b739b78fff6e8cf5cc89ca1cc79d6cdad4858d04d59d1c"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根本原因了：\n\n**问题：** OpenClaw 根本没有配置邮件发送通道！\n\n看 cron 日志里这段：\n```\n\"channel\": \"email\"\n\"error\": \"Error: Telegram send failed: chat not found (chat_id=qn_home@163.com)\"\n```\n\n系统试图用 email 通道发送，但没有 email 插件，就错误地 fallback 到了 Telegram（用邮箱地址作为 chat_id 当然失败）。\n\n**解决方案：** 我来修改 cron 任务，改为：\n1. 生成 HTML 报告 → 保存到文件\n2. 通过 **Telegram** 发送给你（而不是邮件）\n\n这样你每天早上能在 Telegram 收到资讯，不需要配置复杂的 SMTP。\n\n要我改成 Telegram 发送吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":11678,"output":336,"cacheRead":11401,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23415,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771727447033}}
{"type":"message","id":"1cafcd9e","parentId":"e3ca1663","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:38:34.094Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"214\",\n  \"sender\": \"5889732065\"\n}\n```\n\n好，改为发 telegram"}],"timestamp":1771727914091}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5c3fce2","parentId":"1cafcd9e","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:38:38.226Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to change the cron job to send to Telegram instead of email. Let me update the cron job to deliver via Telegram.","thinkingSignature":"530b48b0987bae9b0b7eea961a48cd745f93075572f53b4b37d7fde056724198"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k93rwif4ok80_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron edit 31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9 --channel telegram --to \"5889732065\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":94,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":21914,"totalTokens":22036,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771727914093}}
{"type":"message","id":"43c96d5b","parentId":"e5c3fce2","timestamp":"2026-02-22T02:38:41.308Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k93rwif4ok80_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"name\": \"A股每日资讯\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1771426816719,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1771727921204,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"expr\": \"10 9 * * *\",\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日期。\\n\\n【重要要求】\\n1. 【关键】只抓取过去24小时内的新闻（例如，今天是2026年2月20日，所以只抓取2月19日至2月20日的资讯，不要抓取2月18日及更早的新闻！）\\n2. 必须从【至少4个不同来源】抓取资讯：第一财经、东方财富、新浪财经、同花顺、财联社、每日经济新闻等\\n3. 【不要放链接】- 将资讯要点直接总结展示在邮件正文中，每条资讯需要包含【标题+100字左右的内容摘要】\\n4. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-final.html 作为样式模板\\n5. 每个板块至少精选【TOP 10条】重要资讯（必须是最新24小时内的）\\n6. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\\n7. 【邮件发送】：必须以MIME text/html 格式发送邮件，确保邮件显示为渲染后的HTML页面\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n    \"to\": \"5889732065\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771809000000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1771722600005,\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 600021,\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 6,\n    \"lastError\": \"Error: cron: job execution timed out\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3074,"aggregated":"{\n  \"id\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"name\": \"A股每日资讯\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1771426816719,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1771727921204,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"expr\": \"10 9 * * *\",\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日期。\\n\\n【重要要求】\\n1. 【关键】只抓取过去24小时内的新闻（例如，今天是2026年2月20日，所以只抓取2月19日至2月20日的资讯，不要抓取2月18日及更早的新闻！）\\n2. 必须从【至少4个不同来源】抓取资讯：第一财经、东方财富、新浪财经、同花顺、财联社、每日经济新闻等\\n3. 【不要放链接】- 将资讯要点直接总结展示在邮件正文中，每条资讯需要包含【标题+100字左右的内容摘要】\\n4. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-final.html 作为样式模板\\n5. 每个板块至少精选【TOP 10条】重要资讯（必须是最新24小时内的）\\n6. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\\n7. 【邮件发送】：必须以MIME text/html 格式发送邮件，确保邮件显示为渲染后的HTML页面\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n    \"to\": \"5889732065\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771809000000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1771722600005,\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 600021,\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 6,\n    \"lastError\": \"Error: cron: job execution timed out\"\n  }\n}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771727921305}}
