普关税政策被驳回、港股AI/机器人暴涨、黄金价格创新高等重要资讯。\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1771636200006,\n      \"durationMs\": 528684,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771722600000,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.5\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 1863871,\n        \"output_tokens\": 13566,\n        \"total_tokens\": 64357\n      },\n      \"sessionId\": \"d3982948-bec3-4369-a0b3-40373c8f038d\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:cron:31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9:run:d3982948-bec3-4369-a0b3-40373c8f038d\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1771723200037,\n      \"jobId\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"error\",\n      \"error\": \"Error: cron: job execution timed out\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1771722600005,\n      \"durationMs\": 600021,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771809000000\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2828,"aggregated":"{\n  \"entries\": [\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1771579982471,\n      \"jobId\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"error\",\n      \"error\": \"Error: Telegram send failed: chat not found (chat_id=qn_home@163.com). Likely: bot not started in DM, bot removed from group/channel, group migrated (new -100… id), or wrong bot token. Input was: \\\"qn_home@163.com\\\".\",\n      \"summary\": \"⚠️ 🛠️ Exec: `echo \\\"Test email\\\" | mail -v -s \\\"Test\\\" qn_home@163.com 2>&1` failed: mail: unrecognized option '-v'\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1771579512443,\n      \"durationMs\": 470021,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771636200000,\n      \"sessionId\": \"ea36dc34-c482-4999-937e-6ab5018f8399\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:cron:31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9:run:ea36dc34-c482-4999-937e-6ab5018f8399\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1771636728705,\n      \"jobId\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"error\",\n   